{
  "title": "Flujogramas de Manejo de Patología Neurológica",
  "guid": "17E7CFE40FA8BE5B0F100859",
  "filepath": "/sessions/bold-jolly-cerf/mnt/Dropbox/- Esquemas/- Entidades clínicas/Neurología/Flujogramas de Manejo de Patología Neurológica-2024-1.smmx",
  "root": {
    "id": "0",
    "parent": "-1",
    "text": "Flujogramas de Manejo de\nPatología Neurológica",
    "guid": "In7TlgZ_G2srtXPOH7yb_g",
    "children": [
      {
        "id": "1",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "Criterios de Ingreso Unidad de Paciente Neurocrítico\n(UTIN H2)",
        "guid": "Dqv8mHWM9oFiKdx6MzQAVQ",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "2",
            "parent": "1",
            "text": "1. Neurológicos",
            "guid": "Z1JlkHvDVylHXkojLR592w",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "3",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "a. Guillain Barré y variantes",
                "guid": "LGYr5yhTlcVmf69XN2AIlw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "4",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "b. Crisis miasténica",
                "guid": "ek1K6i8uR4Idw5nKY_G6Ww",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "5",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "c. Encefalitis herpética o autoinmune",
                "guid": "bEZ93zzecLFTDrPyH1j3bA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "6",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "d. Infarto encefálico extenso y/o de comportamiento maligno\n(ACM completa / PICA)",
                "guid": "Io_l2UbRKrBt9S3zLhS9LQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "7",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "e. Hemorragia intracerebral con requerimientos de intervención quirúrgica",
                "guid": "Dp8NDGslk0IdvmBaTYALFQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "8",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "f. Status epiléptico",
                "guid": "Aw1jJy1nHrZckBNvJYw2vQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "9",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "g. Epilepsia descompensada con necesidad de monitorización clínica y EEG",
                "guid": "M-Y6IQhFhz1FSNK8Gzifsg",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "10",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "h. Trombosis venosa cerebral",
                "guid": "BAjeZgynHN9IVx2NMG8KTQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "11",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "i. Enfermedad desmielinizante que requiera tratamiento inmunomodulador o PLEX",
                "guid": "NPqypS7WzORnzxLkL0f9jw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "12",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "j. Realización de test de Katzman",
                "guid": "XgUUZgWSrK8TObfqSkuSRQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "13",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "k. Monitorización EEG continuo electivo",
                "guid": "QnEdYGZIa91ppImxZQEDOQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "14",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "l. Infusión de medicamentos biológicos (Alemtuzumab, Ocrelizumab, entre otros)",
                "guid": "LRmWjVeZt6QTFcBnO7ijmQ",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "15",
            "parent": "1",
            "text": "2. Neuroquirúrgicos",
            "guid": "Qr9K5zDUIMEJOK6vRcyuDg",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "16",
                "parent": "15",
                "text": "a. Hemorragia subaracnoidea",
                "guid": "Xjs_d2XIwh5rWOTLEiF5mQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "17",
                "parent": "15",
                "text": "b. Tumores sistema nervioso central descompensados o postoperados",
                "guid": "bg5JWzCht4ctWhlLchcnwQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "18",
                "parent": "15",
                "text": "c. Traumatismo encefalocraneano moderado/grave o complicado",
                "guid": "PUjUZ3WxNtgihjIPckOHDA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "19",
                "parent": "15",
                "text": "d. Trauma raquimedular o cirugía de columna traumática",
                "guid": "JIgDvQpVRPMhi4SbAo0YIw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "20",
                "parent": "15",
                "text": "e. Manejo de drenaje ventricular o espinal",
                "guid": "D-fxojTFPIVM2KppUlkPAg",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "21",
                "parent": "15",
                "text": "f. Manejo postoperatorio de macroadenoma hipofisiario",
                "guid": "Gw2oYjZ9NBo3WhI8SCc-7w",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "22",
                "parent": "15",
                "text": "g. Infecciones SNC asociados a intervención quirúrgica",
                "guid": "Dhbrv0pv0qMD3-KJUNY2pg",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "23",
                "parent": "15",
                "text": "h. Manejo postquirúrgico de dispositivos de estimulación cerebral",
                "guid": "e0PzZA0YkTgWouS0WX8y3A",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "24",
                "parent": "15",
                "text": "i. Manejo post procedimiento de Neurorradiología intervencional\n(embolización, coils, diversor de flujo, stent, diagnósticas según necesidad)",
                "guid": "cuFTVgH7yX9roKx1YO-csQ",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "25",
            "parent": "1",
            "text": "**Pacientes con criterios UTI neuro pero sin disponibilidad de camas,\ntienen indicación de cama UTI médica (no UTAC)",
            "guid": "VFmWpWC4RB03y2tvOEa3ng",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "26",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "Criterios de Ingreso Unidad de Tratamiento del Ataque Cerebrovascular\n(UTAC H5)",
        "guid": "Mp2BBxj6xcBTBsRyb-ZVbg",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "27",
            "parent": "26",
            "text": "1. ACV en ventana de trombolisis",
            "guid": "f-I7dQO1YRU1wRh5D8otFw",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "28",
            "parent": "26",
            "text": "2. TIA alto riesgo < 3 días",
            "guid": "OHqdmgKZwuJiIzwaU4hF_Q",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "29",
            "parent": "26",
            "text": "3. Infarto lacunar < 3 días",
            "guid": "ORb2_Bl9TlYbr4TsRy3iuw",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "30",
            "parent": "26",
            "text": "4. Infarto cerebral extenso < 5 días no maligno",
            "guid": "Y-0g-R-PZ3UYBBlhXzEUXQ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "31",
            "parent": "26",
            "text": "5. Infarto de tronco < 5 días",
            "guid": "LKf4rS6m_hU4sEc5H4lMAw",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "32",
            "parent": "26",
            "text": "6. Infarto bulbar < 7 días",
            "guid": "MKLHlSRQ864AeOi0Y0BInA",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "33",
            "parent": "26",
            "text": "7. Infarto cerebeloso AICA o SUCA\n(PICA sólo a criterio de neurólogo IC)",
            "guid": "PUu5blN_rSdTJp4KS_e2Bw",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "34",
            "parent": "26",
            "text": "8. Hemorragia intracerebral < 3 días o con\nrequerimientos de antihipertensivos IV",
            "guid": "SQyjqDVQeoR_K7ZcSO7fHQ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "35",
            "parent": "26",
            "text": "9. Trombosis venosa cerebral\n(con o sin infarto asociado)",
            "guid": "OQXbmTTsztVYuQw1cYB5Mw",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "36",
            "parent": "26",
            "text": "*Pacientes con criterios UTAC pero sin disponibilidad de camas,\ntienen indicación de cama UTIN (no UTI médica)",
            "guid": "N4aRtzrcSE9FCL8wcJ2ItA",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "37",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "Flujograma Vasoespasmo\nSintomático",
        "guid": "AEerkk_PhNEXd8v7LO-kQA",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "38",
            "parent": "37",
            "text": "Elementos clínicos de\nvasoespasmo sintomático",
            "guid": "IaQIA2Nu8sgQI6YqbKsqOg",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "39",
                "parent": "38",
                "text": "Territorio Vascular\nElementos Clínicos",
                "guid": "IHGGH2WAMSF9vHZZaX4pxw",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "40",
                    "parent": "39",
                    "text": "Arteria Cerebral Anterior y\nComunicante Anterior",
                    "guid": "GtCrpXzoLLUybQjlU9aHPg",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "41",
                        "parent": "40",
                        "text": "Cuadro confusional no explicable por otra causa",
                        "guid": "RgJdaQpfv6JZ-RX2Glv0Dg",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "42",
                        "parent": "40",
                        "text": "Síndrome febril no explicado",
                        "guid": "axgDvxHEgWZSoqusa1-vUg",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "43",
                        "parent": "40",
                        "text": "Apatía, abulia inatención",
                        "guid": "YZQGN2oad6cYT1OSYAqJHQ",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "44",
                        "parent": "40",
                        "text": "Cambios conductuales con agresividad o retraimiento",
                        "guid": "OkKK3GTIQ9UPI9OZLruRwA",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "45",
                        "parent": "40",
                        "text": "Hemiparesia disarmónica de predominio crural",
                        "guid": "MboczSF9ZrBggFISUiui7A",
                        "children": []
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "46",
                    "parent": "39",
                    "text": "Arteria Cerebral\nMedia",
                    "guid": "Bv2X0l48yGs7qcy0Ic5Ddw",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "47",
                        "parent": "46",
                        "text": "Hemiparesia contralateral\ndisarmónica de predominio crural",
                        "guid": "WyT1IG4W1Zl1pMq2DPnwqw",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "48",
                        "parent": "46",
                        "text": "Afasia (si lado izquierdo)",
                        "guid": "eTzqszr7yyh2VX3uPz9IHA",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "49",
                        "parent": "46",
                        "text": "Hipoalgesia contralateral",
                        "guid": "RVuKylBOk-RZmzwqMHOOig",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "50",
                        "parent": "46",
                        "text": "Hemianopsia homónima contralateral",
                        "guid": "YhMVSiw959Yb0z3cQ6cbgQ",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "51",
                        "parent": "46",
                        "text": "Heminegligencia (si lado derecho)",
                        "guid": "FlhffTQikW4jsaSfUJrqWg",
                        "children": []
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "52",
                    "parent": "39",
                    "text": "Arteria Cerebral\nPosterior",
                    "guid": "GOrVQzLVeDh_VnwaSqTyEQ",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "53",
                        "parent": "52",
                        "text": "Hemianopsia homónima contralateral\n(que respeta visión macular)",
                        "guid": "VFLe6F_Wziwc0JT9W1B2ug",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "54",
                        "parent": "52",
                        "text": "Amaurosis (si compromiso bilateral)",
                        "guid": "PhOWl1h6YbF9HroyGTiLtw",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "55",
                        "parent": "52",
                        "text": "Cefalea",
                        "guid": "RpE3SnLDhOgmMnxjP84h_Q",
                        "children": []
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "56",
                    "parent": "39",
                    "text": "Arteria Basilar y\nVertebrales",
                    "guid": "Lb9QEByH-lF_DWoZcxra2g",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "57",
                        "parent": "56",
                        "text": "Disartria",
                        "guid": "bNaONViopkMjjmlkTumjgA",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "58",
                        "parent": "56",
                        "text": "Nistagmus",
                        "guid": "BOaOGT9hp0ASkL8BGz7tlw",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "59",
                        "parent": "56",
                        "text": "Compromiso de conciencia",
                        "guid": "c4Q4rjZCY6Br2dfxDG8N8g",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "60",
                        "parent": "56",
                        "text": "Cefalea",
                        "guid": "aRfb2GswVAtXFAADPWq6wQ",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "61",
                        "parent": "56",
                        "text": "Ataxia",
                        "guid": "SwciN3PklQAYuzF7CRq4zg",
                        "children": []
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "62",
                "parent": "38",
                "text": "Simuladores de\nVasoespasmo",
                "guid": "TF72shXZ660iU0SFEvAt_A",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "63",
                    "parent": "62",
                    "text": "Hidrocefalia",
                    "guid": "CJ1wlUiFwOhSvk_6NlzApQ",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "64",
                    "parent": "62",
                    "text": "Fiebre de origen infeccioso",
                    "guid": "ZQ27OVHLuhMpd5uAUeRJbw",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "65",
                    "parent": "62",
                    "text": "Edema con hipertensión intracraniana",
                    "guid": "KnRgV00GBOQgzezvL1rucA",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "66",
                    "parent": "62",
                    "text": "Hipo/hipernatremia",
                    "guid": "DGesJTNeq_BKmdwHf-vk0w",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "67",
                    "parent": "62",
                    "text": "Crisis convulsiva",
                    "guid": "aaEPkTZzs_gMWvLFUrjraQ",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "68",
            "parent": "37",
            "text": "Objetivar\nVasoespasmo",
            "guid": "dHkG40zx2PgSWZMXMcTAUg",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "69",
                "parent": "68",
                "text": "Objetivar vasoespasmo mediante\nDTC, angioTC o angiografía",
                "guid": "WoxJyBFusdJDERTZIv9vPQ",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "70",
            "parent": "37",
            "text": "Manejo",
            "guid": "UpA_JkPgZYdXMBqwE0etzg",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "71",
                "parent": "70",
                "text": "Inicial",
                "guid": "RTPcIGC_W7IKCLHDU2Zraw",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "72",
                    "parent": "71",
                    "text": "PAM más de 20% del basal",
                    "guid": "V1OHySje16Z1xeMII7J-ew",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "73",
                        "parent": "72",
                        "text": "(ideal sobre 100-120)",
                        "guid": "PrjDUxgZJ442oqx3R1Yz6Q",
                        "children": []
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "74",
                    "parent": "71",
                    "text": "Corrección del Medio interno",
                    "guid": "YJ7odglg_HF9svSORayjsA",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "75",
                        "parent": "74",
                        "text": "Hipovolemia, hipertermia,\nhiponatremia, hipomagnasemia",
                        "guid": "EmYdrlh3UwdR5wYvfEgGzQ",
                        "children": []
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "76",
                    "parent": "71",
                    "text": "Descartar Factores Contundentes",
                    "guid": "Wyy2hScqkA4XkO0fBaEW3A",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "77",
                "parent": "70",
                "text": "Reevaluación Clínica\ncada 30-60 minutos",
                "guid": "dDCU8zhe2g40_AVMAJhBGA",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "78",
                    "parent": "77",
                    "text": "Persiste Déficit",
                    "guid": "NgmVTAzfGLEoF4D5V62dUA",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "79",
                        "parent": "78",
                        "text": "Titular NAD para PAM 120-130",
                        "guid": "cE4LeTg7JyNEWMeKR6GTQg",
                        "children": []
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "80",
                    "parent": "77",
                    "text": "Persiste Déficit",
                    "guid": "YRn-yToeqpNrVBG9H9LCHQ",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "81",
                        "parent": "80",
                        "text": "Manejo Vasoespasmo Refractario",
                        "guid": "UjfSISH2vjVnKPYGMta6lw",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "82",
                        "parent": "80",
                        "text": "Angioplastía de\nEmergencia",
                        "guid": "K1e6pmTb6pR4g15HBoRxKw",
                        "children": [
                          {
                            "id": "83",
                            "parent": "82",
                            "text": "Factible",
                            "guid": "DAZ6oxAUS2YMJYgHADcPlg",
                            "children": [
                              {
                                "id": "84",
                                "parent": "83",
                                "text": "Traslado Pabellón Hemodinamia",
                                "guid": "QLduqAFTdpkJj0ECdsED9A",
                                "children": []
                              }
                            ]
                          },
                          {
                            "id": "85",
                            "parent": "82",
                            "text": "No Factible",
                            "guid": "SHMldEEhjVQAz1CuNDCrcw",
                            "children": [
                              {
                                "id": "86",
                                "parent": "85",
                                "text": "Protocolo Milrinona",
                                "guid": "aeHpHxLHaM9GIi4GSvvn6A",
                                "children": []
                              }
                            ]
                          }
                        ]
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "87",
                "parent": "70",
                "text": "Flujograma Milrinona en\nVasoespasmo Sintomático",
                "guid": "az671hgJNDVHQ-61OCTPOA",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "88",
                    "parent": "87",
                    "text": "Asegurar PAM 100-120 con NAD",
                    "guid": "SX9z-TISmLtXQrS7HOxx8g",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "89",
                    "parent": "87",
                    "text": "Milrinona Intravenosa",
                    "guid": "BAo4xik3VNYbsSqSOt3DZg",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "90",
                        "parent": "89",
                        "text": "Iniciar Milrinona a 0.5 mcg/kg/min",
                        "guid": "c69TOCD6VF19t8ipTjudAA",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "91",
                        "parent": "89",
                        "text": "Persiste Déficit",
                        "guid": "esD3728qkMQ32KcbZf-zxQ",
                        "children": [
                          {
                            "id": "92",
                            "parent": "91",
                            "text": "Ascenso gradual en 0.25 mcg/kg/min",
                            "guid": "MmkGL0DI3YJxOww9BPlFVg",
                            "children": []
                          }
                        ]
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "93",
                        "parent": "89",
                        "text": "Persiste Déficit",
                        "guid": "BzPE-X8cldAeJIL-ULM48w",
                        "children": [
                          {
                            "id": "94",
                            "parent": "93",
                            "text": "Titular hasta 1.25 mcg/kg/min dosis máxima",
                            "guid": "BKlDCUhrJu0YQPMkSd0fKg",
                            "children": []
                          }
                        ]
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "95",
                    "parent": "87",
                    "text": "Consideraciones",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "96",
                        "parent": "95",
                        "text": "Siempre priorizar PAM sobre uso de milrinona.",
                        "guid": "MS8ui3VnN7ltn6rlNTlnUg",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "97",
                        "parent": "95",
                        "text": "Si respuesta inodilatadora tras uso de milrinona genera hipotensión relativa,\nsuspender y priorizar vasopresor",
                        "guid": "Kksp1G3O82JgiXzIXLQwBA",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "98",
                        "parent": "95",
                        "text": "En caso de iniciar milrinona, siempre asegurar mínimo PAM 90-100,\ncon vasopresor de ser necesario",
                        "guid": "Hp6MjwlQ1XdwFyq4Ek3fxw",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "99",
                        "parent": "95",
                        "text": "Reevaluar clínicamente cada 60-120 minutos",
                        "guid": "LpfQ5FHEiQVhrXVaM0ET7g",
                        "children": []
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "100",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "Flujograma de Manejo de Crisis Convulsiva\nen Urgencia y Hospitalizados",
        "guid": "HDgNZhphva1-6tLhFvkFVQ",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "101",
            "parent": "100",
            "text": "Crisis de Inicio\nObjetivado",
            "guid": "CYxOcTbDefx8-LkaEMATag",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "102",
                "parent": "101",
                "text": "HGT + Tiamina",
                "guid": "NeAPzBsdPBhhc0xdZw8-WA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "103",
                "parent": "101",
                "text": "Resolución Crisis\ndentro de 3-5 minutos",
                "guid": "EIRz0k8S90McSKWqLyMAYQ",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "104",
                    "parent": "103",
                    "text": "Si → Estudio",
                    "guid": "WGPMugxf0GJBcOApAq72jw",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "105",
                    "parent": "103",
                    "text": "No → Dosis BZD",
                    "guid": "ei7DxCH6XPFfYyaTKMaUqQ",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "106",
                "parent": "101",
                "text": "Resolución crisis\ndentro de 3-5 minutos",
                "guid": "c77l9kEQm-1cB6iXDe6V6Q",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "107",
                    "parent": "106",
                    "text": "Si → Estudio",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "108",
                    "parent": "106",
                    "text": "No → Referirse a Flujograma Status Epiléptico",
                    "guid": "c4eZXFAzm11uMBcmfRPnzQ",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "109",
            "parent": "100",
            "text": "Crisis de Inicio Desconocido\no más de 5 minutos",
            "guid": "BvcVWWso0EEN0_s3PNclJg",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "110",
                "parent": "109",
                "text": "HGT + BZD + Tiamina",
                "guid": "BkYMWW9HR5Uj5mN-FsqAKw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "111",
                "parent": "109",
                "text": "Resolución Crisis\ndentro de 3-5 minutos",
                "guid": "Plo-2EAvCShF7YCNFr4Lkg",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "112",
                    "parent": "111",
                    "text": "Si → Estudio",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "113",
                    "parent": "111",
                    "text": "No → Nueva dosis BZD",
                    "guid": "OeDEoUuL2o8rBjmHdN_JDQ",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "114",
                "parent": "109",
                "text": "Resolución crisis\ndentro de 3-5 minutos",
                "guid": "",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "115",
                    "parent": "114",
                    "text": "Si → Estudio",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "116",
                    "parent": "114",
                    "text": "No → Referirse a Flujograma Status Epiléptico",
                    "guid": "",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "117",
            "parent": "100",
            "text": "Notas",
            "guid": "",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "118",
                "parent": "117",
                "text": "* BZD de\nelección:",
                "guid": "D8wwDgDtxr8HsrtgOSTttQ",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "119",
                    "parent": "118",
                    "text": "* Vía venosa permeable (VPP): Lorazepam IV 0.1 mg/kg (ampolla 4 mg) (1)",
                    "guid": "dGZEhghtz1hngMSeQPUeEQ",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "120",
                    "parent": "118",
                    "text": "* Sin VPP: Midazolam IM 0.2 mg/kg (ampolla 10 mg) (2)",
                    "guid": "eb3vdHc27VhWPJFSM560FQ",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "121",
                "parent": "117",
                "text": "* Tiamina: 90-300 mg (3)",
                "guid": "QsLH5wFCytkofn0iZ3R-JQ",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "122",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "Estudio Crisis\nConvulsiva en Urgencias",
        "guid": "LtxKBhT7BSYdjhz4VEwMTA",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "123",
            "parent": "122",
            "text": "Situaciones que deben ser incluidas en el\n\"Estudio\" de un evento convulsivo:",
            "guid": "devY2U538645fuwteaHPOg",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "124",
                "parent": "123",
                "text": "Mala adherencia a fármacos (niveles séricos de VPA, FNT, FBT, CBZ)",
                "guid": "XehRtz7XCBNM4o4pMyOmLw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "125",
                "parent": "123",
                "text": "↑ Peso (reajuste de fármacos a peso)",
                "guid": "D2vPJB4xU4lAezJsDd-LDg",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "126",
                "parent": "123",
                "text": "Descompensación por foco infeccioso (urinario, respiratorio, meníngeo, faríngeo)",
                "guid": "b4Hz1BhXcKBuaXcvA1S91g",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "127",
                "parent": "123",
                "text": "Descompensante metabólico (hipo/hiperglicemia, hipo/hipernatremia, hipocalcemia, hipomagnesemia, hipofosfatemia)",
                "guid": "c-fLvRuWbRR7CMHsYYQNmw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "128",
                "parent": "123",
                "text": "Encefalopatía hepática/urémica",
                "guid": "aPZwEnIedvxle4r_IHQbNQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "129",
                "parent": "123",
                "text": "Consumo OH o privación",
                "guid": "GkbF9kKRC9JDUjlVHAAr_Q",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "130",
                "parent": "123",
                "text": "Privación de horas de sueño",
                "guid": "YDkON08il09r4AESPiFf7w",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "131",
                "parent": "123",
                "text": "Fármacos que ↓ umbral convulsivante (antibióticos, neurolépticos, etc.)",
                "guid": "DfmfYjjCjztxRQYeHWVuhg",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "132",
                "parent": "123",
                "text": "Realización de TC de cerebro si corresponde",
                "guid": "VvPixDHAOIorRPmURnXWmA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "133",
                "parent": "123",
                "text": "Punción lumbar si todos los factores anteriores resultan normales",
                "guid": "ShepKxmucMRJypRvVZLDAw",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "134",
            "parent": "122",
            "text": "Estudio\nalterado?",
            "guid": "VTtUeFCUxxFRTsVgDVeMPA",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "135",
                "parent": "134",
                "text": "Si",
                "guid": "",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "136",
                    "parent": "135",
                    "text": "GCS<15 o no basal",
                    "guid": "Fls7h2odqCQxEpnqWR4Dbg",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "137",
                        "parent": "136",
                        "text": "Observación/Hospitalización",
                        "guid": "a2By_VmRFw1AkoGTaPI_2g",
                        "children": []
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "138",
                    "parent": "135",
                    "text": "GCS=15 o basal",
                    "guid": "Su_5DgLIL6EXcZLPWrwpHA",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "139",
                        "parent": "138",
                        "text": "Alta Policlínico Primera Crisis o Epilepsia Descompensada",
                        "guid": "A7X2YR8kTi8T4RbRfXPl1Q",
                        "children": []
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "140",
                "parent": "134",
                "text": "No",
                "guid": "TiZvDkBAT1IzBqoYfQK5FA",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "141",
                    "parent": "140",
                    "text": "Puede Manejo\nAmbulatorio?",
                    "guid": "fnO76lFQoEtX3D40YInsIQ",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "142",
                        "parent": "141",
                        "text": "Si",
                        "guid": "bZxB3U1gAv53FbUPA_d9ZA",
                        "children": [
                          {
                            "id": "143",
                            "parent": "142",
                            "text": "Alta Policlínico Primera Crisis o Epilepsia Descompensada",
                            "guid": "N32rIigoTvpdFYDSIt4eIA",
                            "children": []
                          }
                        ]
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "144",
                        "parent": "141",
                        "text": "No",
                        "guid": "AblmBx2oAmUL0F36T9_VFQ",
                        "children": [
                          {
                            "id": "145",
                            "parent": "144",
                            "text": "Observación/Hospitalización",
                            "guid": "E9LKAnMjqTg3BmDfXsLDEA",
                            "children": []
                          }
                        ]
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "146",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "Flujograma de Manejo de\nStatus Epiléptico",
        "guid": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "147",
            "parent": "146",
            "text": "Elegir 1",
            "guid": "RCDunnoFrStQ4w2xXme0lA",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "148",
                "parent": "147",
                "text": "Levetiracetam 30-40 mg/kg (máx 4 g) en 5-10 minutos",
                "guid": "PJa4_RQ1RwZ6Z-CRHM_HNA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "149",
                "parent": "147",
                "text": "Fenitoína 20 mg/kg infusión a 50 mg/minuto",
                "guid": "Y1feVmZH4aNa8ScjcVF9uA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "150",
                "parent": "147",
                "text": "Valproico 30-40 mg/kg infusión a 200 mg/min",
                "guid": "Px5I0yviFVZW-bW1MwYUkA",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "151",
            "parent": "146",
            "text": "Resolución\nClínica",
            "guid": "U6pWlwY-vqkdoNH7Esifag",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "152",
                "parent": "151",
                "text": "Sí",
                "guid": "MiDT_3Sah7BFzrP7eZlWaQ",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "153",
                    "parent": "152",
                    "text": "Traslado Cama UTI/UTIN",
                    "guid": "Rpz_UlpY1iYqCEjmCr3t8A",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "154",
                "parent": "151",
                "text": "No",
                "guid": "VF6DUXrrVpdpJaKEEPU8Tg",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "155",
                    "parent": "154",
                    "text": "Traslado Cama UCI (solicitar EEG precoz/continuo)",
                    "guid": "DyCdnmONgxUtxQODcnh79A",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "156",
                    "parent": "154",
                    "text": "Opción 1",
                    "guid": "SdVkuAi2KqZjyfmsaN_Vlg",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "157",
                        "parent": "156",
                        "text": "Midazolam bolo 0.2 mg/kg, luego infusión 0.1-0.3 mg/kg/h",
                        "guid": "VOxX6HKA5ete3ik4UuK9tQ",
                        "children": []
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "158",
                    "parent": "154",
                    "text": "Opción 2",
                    "guid": "LHzLvxtSU3Ma8MysACciVg",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "159",
                        "parent": "158",
                        "text": "Propofol bolo 1-2 mg/kg, luego infusión 1-3 mg/kg/h",
                        "guid": "IZESHDiRnqcS78HBU7HmHA",
                        "children": []
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "160",
            "parent": "146",
            "text": "Resolución\nClínica",
            "guid": "LSwmWFi-dbxNSzyFc8klqg",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "161",
                "parent": "160",
                "text": "Sí",
                "guid": "MxdL4ndThWt-hxObB3XPNA",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "162",
                    "parent": "161",
                    "text": "Sedación con meta supresión clínica o EEG, por 24 h o hasta resolución de factor causal",
                    "guid": "cj7cA2esth8YawuCAV95oQ",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "163",
                "parent": "160",
                "text": "No",
                "guid": "Szo5NUYwDwVz1_WVFQ-d7Q",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "164",
                    "parent": "163",
                    "text": "Evaluación Neurológica para esquema de tercera línea",
                    "guid": "TuY5rFeh70F973OEI9KRlA",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "165",
            "parent": "146",
            "text": "Notas:",
            "guid": "SiLVLVzNnLx2tU9Jdp-g7A",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "166",
                "parent": "165",
                "text": "* La selección de sedación debe ser realizada considerando antecedentes previos y período estimado de sedación por el tratante.",
                "guid": "eB_wLxGmG_Z2xsNCGbECTA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "167",
                "parent": "165",
                "text": "* Debe considerase inicialmente una dosis de sedoanalgesia suficiente para suprimir clínicamente la actividad epiléptica.",
                "guid": "Sje6nQm2hQNtYuhod2Pg9Q",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "168",
                "parent": "165",
                "text": "* La titulación de la sedación para alcanzar una meta electroencefalográfica de \"Estallido supresión\" (Burst Suppression) o\n\"Beta farmacológico\" debe realizarse únicamente con monitoreo EEG y con evidencia de trazados de status epiléptico.",
                "guid": "YnT6vzquJO1rLQagFYxGog",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
